  "title": "[사당역이수역추나요법/체형교정추나요법잘하는곳]체형교정 치료효과",
  "addDate": "2013. 5. 12.",
  "categoryNo": "14",
  "parentCategoryNo": "7",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=110167954196",
  "html_size": 190843,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view110167954196\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea110167954196\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'>\r\n<div class=\"view\" style='font-family: \"3028548_9\"; font-size: 9pt;'>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">[사당역이수역추나요법/체형교정추나요법잘하는곳]</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">체형교정 치료효과</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추와 골격이 이상적인 정렬을 이룰 때 우리몸의 디스크와 관절은 정상기능을 수행할 수 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">그러나 굽어지거나, 일자가 되거나 틀어지거나 하게 되면 디스크가 눌리거나, </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">관절이 한 쪽만 닳게 되거나 움직일 때마다 소리가 나거나 하는 등 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">기능 및 구조상의 문제가 발생하게 되고, 통증으로 이어집니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ed802ab093aba56e.png\" width=\"487\" height=\"469\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 487px; rheight: 469px;\" id=\"20130512_78/isuhani_1368340537789RUrQe_PNG/%C3%BC%C7%FC%B1%B3%C1%A4.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6859314')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ed802ab093aba56e.png\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">비뚤어진 체형은 통증을 계속해서 재발하게끔 하기 때문에 자세가 나빠서 자꾸 아프게 되는 경우, </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">침치료와 물리치료를 해도 자꾸 다시 아파지는 경우, 자세에 따라서 아픈정도가 달라지는 경우 등은 </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">척추 관절의 정렬이 비뚤어지진 않았는지 확인하고, </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">비뚤어졌으면 바로잡기 위한 교정을 해주어야 합니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d0a115db95849d2.png\" width=\"439\" height=\"278\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 439px; rheight: 278px;\" id=\"20130512_239/isuhani_1368340538882zsfM5_PNG/%C3%BC%C7%FC%B1%B3%C1%A42.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6859314')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/5d0a115db95849d2.png\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">체형교정추나요법 치료는 단 1회만으로도 골격의 정렬이 달라짐을 느낄 수도 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">그러나 하지길이 차이나 척우 골반이 복합적으로 틀어진 경우, </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">턱관절이 같이 틀어진 경우 등은 10여회~ 길게는 30회정도 교정을 해야하는 경우도 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/85eeade25a29f424.png\" width=\"532\" height=\"539\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 532px; rheight: 539px;\" id=\"20130512_60/isuhani_1368340549859kNzYx_PNG/%BE%EE%B1%FA2.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6859314')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/85eeade25a29f424.png\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">목, 허리 디스크, 어깨, 무릎 관절통, 만성적인 목, 어깨, 허리 통증, 팔 다리 저림, 만성피로, </span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">집중력 저하, 만성두통, 여성의 자궁질환(생리통), 등이 체형지료의 대상이 됩니다.</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><br style=\"clear: both;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/900f216528d4df74.png\" width=\"302\" height=\"198\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rwidth: 302px; rheight: 198px;\" id=\"20130512_195/isuhani_1368340550873Y2eOO_PNG/%BE%EE%B1%FA4.PNG\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_0000000000000019A6859314')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/900f216528d4df74.png\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">체형교정추나요법&nbsp; 이수한의원에서는&nbsp; 추나요법 잘 하는곳으로 차별화된 체형교정 치료를 임하고 있습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">특히 산후로 골반의 뒤틀림으로 여러가지 통증을 호소 하는 경우가 많습니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;뒤틀렸던 골반을 교정 함으로써 통증완화 및 체형이 잘 잡히게 됩니다</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><pzp-pc-layout class=\"_naverVideo _vnl\" vid=\"38B7EA7891F8100E087DBA0540DD5B8EF599\" key=\"V121102b822c99064c565d0d35e98ea296cc1874c2b59a79916505f6ec61857d1ef83d0d35e98ea296cc1\" outKeyMode=\"false\" hasLink=\"true\" logNo=\"110167954196\" domain-or-blogId=\"isuhani\" style=\"width:512px; height:321px;\">\n  <pzp-pc-header class=\"pzp-pc__header\">\n    <pzp-pc-content-info class=\"pzp-pc__content-info\">\n      <pzp-pc-content-title></pzp-pc-content-title>\n      <pzp-pc-play-count></pzp-pc-play-count>\n    </pzp-pc-content-info>\n    <pzp-pc-toolbar class=\"pzp-pc__toolbar\">\n        <pzp-pc-share-button class=\"pzp-pc__share-button\" data-style=\"type_player\" data-player-target-id=\"spi_player_38B7EA7891F8100E087DBA0540DD5B8EF599\"></pzp-pc-share-button>\n    </pzp-pc-toolbar>\n  </pzp-pc-header>\n<span id=\"spi_player_38B7EA7891F8100E087DBA0540DD5B8EF599\" class=\"pzp-pc__social-plugin-container\"></span>\n</pzp-pc-layout>\n</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 162); font-family: 돋움,Dotum; font-size: 11pt;\">&lt;체형교정추나요법 이수한의원 진료시간안내&gt;</span></strong></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazon